sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as 🌐 User
  participant E as 🔐 Azure Easy Auth and Auth0
  participant S as 📊 Streamlit Dashboard
  participant M as 🧩 gems modules
  participant D as 🗄️ Databricks SQL
  participant K as 🔑 Azure Table Storage

  U->>E: Open dashboard and sign in
  E-->>S: Authenticated identity with email claims
  S->>M: require_authorized_user checks users and domains
  U->>S: Select API Access Chat Explore or Modeling
  alt API Access
    S->>K: Create list or revoke hashed API keys
    K-->>S: Key metadata and one time raw key on create
  else Explore or Modeling
    S->>M: Fetch and cache allowed gold table data
    M->>D: Query gems_catalog.gold_v1 with PAT
    D-->>M: Rows and schema
  else Chat
    S->>M: Compose context and prompt
    M-->>S: AI answer using configured OpenAI model
  end
  S-->>U: Render tables charts scripts or chat response
